  "texts": [
    "For comparison, it took other consumer internet applications, such as Facebook and Instagram, four and a half and two and a half years, respectively, to reach the 100 million users.",
    "Meanwhile, more traditional technologies, like mobile phones and the internet, required sixteen and seven years, respectively [24].",
    "Since 2022, GenAI has boomed and an ever-growing number of GenAI tools are publicly available and actively used by politicians, teachers, students and entire companies that are building their business models around it [33].",
    "Oftentimes, the implementation of GenAI is seen as beneficial, as it improves efficiency and can boost productivity.",
    "In the academic world, however, it sparked a \"can you describe what you are\"."
  ]
}